	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />It's not uncommon for space shooters to have seemingly nonsensical names like Salamander.<br />But, focusing the setting from &quot;space&quot; to some specific field or portion of space could help with inspiration for a title.<br />You could also present some genre twist or key gameplay feature to help with a title too. <br /><br />Ship tilting animation looks good, btw.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


	<hr width="85%" />

